name: electron expander
description:
in a forgotten past, humans would travel the road bearing gifts and offerings to pay homage to the cultures they visited. researchers say that seasoned technomancers could manipulate the antimatter within certain objects to increase their size, hoping a once small contribution would produce a greater reward.

cast to invoke opulence. inscribed by tenorless circa 2022 // elements collection [earth]

one of three artifacts from technomancy beta test 0.1
